name: I Finally Visited St. Maarten!
description:
The Caribbean island of Saint Martin/Sint Maarten is an iconic vacation destination and home to just over 70,000 people.

It's also a bucket list destination for aviation enthusiasts, made famous for the low landings over Maho Beach at the end of the runway at Princess Juliana International Airport.

After saving up for a while, an opportunity came up to go and I booked a vacation there for February last year.

So, join me, as I spend a week in paradise and see what this amazing island has to offer!
